Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奠定了集权制官僚国家基础的圣德太子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他是否真的存在表示质疑的人也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个圣德太子骑着马飞上天空去了富士山的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}少骗人了 新井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}马怎么可能会飞上天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从富士山回来之后 我有些不敢看日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向好像也很少见的顾虑我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们这样的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.50,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(570,426)}致我亲爱的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得收拾下背包里面呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头灯结果都没用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候买的玩偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个羊羹 那是日向的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊 葵她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后就没了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短信我也不知道该怎么发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是枫在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去北阿尔卑斯纵走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去穿越大岩棱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去见见葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 现在还是不要去管她的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:04:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 她一定会打起精神来的 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会打给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是暑假 我却无所事事 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起 心里就好像裂开了一个大口子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管做什么都不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和心夏写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从富士山邮寄到这里 是现在到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很热的 戴上帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天览山 高尾山 三增峠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还来了富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天再一起去回忆中的大山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么日向写的这么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 葵 爬哪个山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始爬那边的小山丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样随便呢 不受欢迎的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟受不受欢迎没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近处的小山丘的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会遇难的哦 我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么害怕 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前明明还上气不接下气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比以前还能爬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像散步一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前是走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这边走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有点陡峭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经登顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才明信片寄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为写着天览山 就有点怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散步 真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算等下去多峰主山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多峰主山?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这前面也有大山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说 从这里开始才是真正的登山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(662,446)}注意蝮蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里叫做回首坡道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说很久很久以前有位大人在这里回了好几次头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天空树啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尾山也看得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去了那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后 我心里一直像裂开了一个大口子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样也非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我还是想再登山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那我们一起登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的 一点一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 也能登上回忆中的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的 摔倒了再爬起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一个人很痛苦 有肯陪伴我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃羊羹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向之前给我的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为羊羹啊 你是老爷爷么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是你买的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一步一步 慢慢来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是一点一点 只要向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为总有一天 双脚会到达山顶的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见 yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:07.64,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}並んで歩いてたら 自然に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:11.60,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}二人三脚なってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:18.36,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}透明リボンで結ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.28,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一人で描く夢は……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.49,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}ふたりなら立体的になる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.29,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}キュンときて上昇! 行こう!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.16,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}スタッカートみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:38.09,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:38.92,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}それに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.47,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}付き合ってくれる　俺の合う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.80,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.14,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}地球色パレット
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.10,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}混ぜて明日は何色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.02,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.19,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不安より楽しみの容量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:04.53,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.11,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天ヤッホー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:07.64,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}两人并肩行走 自然地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:11.60,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}变成了两人三脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:18.36,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}透明的缎带将我们紧紧连结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.28,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}就算是一人所描绘的梦想……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.49,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}两个人的话就会变得可以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.25,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}心跳正在加速！一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.16,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}像那跳跃的音符一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:38.09,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}敲击心灵的兴奋感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:38.92,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}还有那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.47,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}在我身旁陪着我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.80,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.14,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}地球色的调色板上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.10,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天又是属于何种颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.02,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不可思议的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.19,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}比起不安 开心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:04.53,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}却渐渐高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.11,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天见 呀吼
